Revision history for CSS-Tiny-Style

0.0.3_01
        - changes by Barbie
        - added AUTOMATED_TESTING check to tests not requuired for user install
        - split CSS::Tiny out from CSS::Tiny::Style as duplicate package 
          declarations were causing prerequisites errors. now called 
          CSS::Tiny::Styles and uses CSS::Tiny as a base.
        - added missing dependencies.
        - fixed errors/warnings as suggested by Perl::critic tests.
        - incorporated patch RT#28718 from Tokuhiro Matsuno 
        - added extra test file, providing basic tests of the modules
        - fixed selector match for "a:hover".

0.0.1  Wed Jan 24 20:09:53 2007
       Initial release.

